'''Janice''' is the mother of [[Lolly]].

==History==
Janice's daughter, Lolly, was acting sick after coming home from the park, so she used an app to call a doctor. Richard arrived and Janice explained what was happening. When Richard went to assess Lolly, she vomited on him. Janice then said Lolly probably had the flu, which Richard agreed with.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She was worried when her daughter started acting sick, so she used an app to call a doctor to their home.

==Notes and Trivia==
*She has a dog named Dumbledore.
